title: Under The Red Star
description:
Under the Red Star (2011)
 
https://i.imgur.com/wbnr158.jpg


The Finnish Labour Temple opened in March 1910, but it was a temple of a different sort, one where political, rather than religious devotion, was practiced. Under the Red Star tells the story of union organizers, strong minded women, athletic children, actors and even poets. This docu-drama brings to life the lively and dramatic past of the early years of Finnish immigration to Canada.
